content: When I tried to edit the profile of a repo distro it just kep crashing. Couldn't find anything about that in the docs. Tried just running install, but that was a noop. So I thought, maybe it's all pre-configured and all I need to do is start the container. When I did that it errored out saying TARGET_PATH wasn't set. I assume that var is configured in the profile, which, as I said, I could not edit due to crash. Refunded, sorry.
